* steady and unsteady problems.
* 
* Example usage:
*
* errordriver(10,2,4,4,1/3,'D',0,'D',-2*tanh(1),0.1,'irk1','BurgersVisc','SS')
* 
* errordriver(20,2,4,4,1,'D',0,'D',0,0.1,'icn','Poisson','TimeAccurate')
**********************************************/